            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-vmark="d7c3">IT之家 4 月 20 日消息，WIKO 情感陪伴 AI 电子宠物“智能憨憨”蜂窝版今日官宣上市，支持 Wi-Fi / 蜂窝网络，<strong>新品预售价 499 元</strong>，将在 4 月 25 日正式开售。</p><p data-vmark="876a" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/2bbe295d-ef63-4c05-ad21-341b4c4a7b09.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1440" h="2880" data-weibo="0" data-mpos="0,0" data-marks="1931fd9d012eb6d148fb5305852f59ed9eeedf120d14468d44c5136a3431e9496e501fdd1690fb2b1fa2df33abbd78bd" data-vmark="0b0d"></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/ja4snoa" target="_blank" data-wapurl="https://u.jd.com/ja4Q5B2" data-iosurl="https://u.jd.com/jO4QDQd" data-androidurl="https://u.jd.com/jO4OLaU" data-hosnexturl="https://u.jd.com/jG41LVL" data-hosurl="https://u.jd.com/jO4I16L" data-uwpurl="https://u.jd.com/jDxohpB" data-wxmpurl="ithome://openmp?appid=wx91d27dbf599dff74&amp;path=%2fpages%2funion%2fproxy%2fproxy%3fspreadUrl%3dhttps%253a%252f%252fu.jd.com%252fjG4d6Mp%26EA_PTAG%3d17078.27.380" data-itwxurl="https://u.jd.com/jg4Maqm" data-lpwxurl="https://u.jd.com/jr4u0LX"  data-jdid="BNVjhQZ2171ku6w47o1BqcfEWr_385VbR6F7DNT8BYmEs" data-ncid="157862"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/421766/24/4185/129428/69e20df5F3b1cddf8/00833203203e8aaf.png" w="800" h="800"></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> WIKO 情感陪伴 AI 电子宠物“智能憨憨”</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">499 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p data-vmark="dcfe" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/84de8daa-c5b3-4fd8-bd1a-6611b7eb1e2b.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="882" h="3086" data-mpos="2,2"  data-vmark="ed2c"></p><p data-vmark="6fe8">IT之家注意到，<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/900/499.htm